The winter sport community in Singapore and other Southeast Asian countries has been growing for the past few years, with majority of the people heading to nearby countries like Japan and South Korea. Indoor ski simulators are also gaining popularity for those who are preparing for their ski holidays. For skiers and snowboarders who are keen on exploring Europe, look no further than St. Anton ski resort in Austria. Experience the ultimate ski and snowboard trip in Austria with Alpenature. We also offer customised packages to your preferences, and cover everything from accommodation to food and transport. 
